name: Rash Decision T Shirt SEAGULL
description: New Rash Decision SEAGULL T Shirt. Available in black or white. High quality prints on Gildan shirts. Designed by Tim Ryan. Available in Small, medium, large and extra large.

name: Rash Decision Hats
description:
Hats come in two types: Green Trucker Hat & Black Baseball Cap

All the hats were bought and then had the Rash Decision patches sewn on by hand by my girlfriend who hates me now because she realised it takes almost half an hour per hat. Please buy them so I can make her do more so we can yell at each other because we both enjoy that.

They also come with a free RD badge and a Dammit badge. Dammit were a band I started when I was 14 and I have lots of badges left. To be honest it's just an excuse to get them out of my flat. Enjoy.

One size fits all unless there's something wrong with you.
